      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ICE AGE (1) is a quick dog who thrives over the short dashes. Last start was fourth over 342m at Angle Park in a Grade 4 (19.83). Hard to go past form here at this journey. Is yet to miss the placings from this draw, including six wins, from nine starts. Has ability and can bounce back. SECRET SUPER (8) has a strong record here with two wins and three placings from six starts. Comes off a (16.83) win last time, scoring by a nose in a Grade 4/5 over 300m at this track. Can hit the frame with the right run. DARK MOONSHINE (2) last appeared when too good (23.08) over 400m at Gawler on November 16. Resumes after finishing fifth (23.08) at Gawler over 400m five months ago. Has a good record here including six wins. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. TECHNO KELLI (4) has claims fresh from a recent placing in a tight finish.",
